    public abstract class CodegenRecorderBuildable<PatternDescription>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Buildable<PatternDescription,java.lang.String,java.lang.String>
    Lightweight class that generates Java code of a builder method from the build actions. Code is sent to a coordinator to be collected in string buffers there.
